{"format":"tiptap/v1","updatedAt":"2026-06-21T17:49:13.184Z","doc":{"type":"doc","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Extended Thinking"},{"type":"text","text":" is Claude's enhanced reasoning capability that lets the model work through complex problems step-by-step before delivering its final answer, while providing transparency into its internal thought process."}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"What It Is"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Extended Thinking gives Claude a \"scratchpad\" to reason through problems deliberately. When enabled, Claude outputs its internal reasoning in "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"code"}],"text":"thinking"},{"type":"text","text":" content blocks, incorporates insights from that reasoning, then crafts a final response in "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"code"}],"text":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" content blocks."}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Why It Matters"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Without extended thinking, Claude responds quickly with near-instant answers. With it, Claude self-reflects before answering, which significantly improves performance on math, physics, instruction-following, coding, and other tasks requiring deep reasoning."}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Key Benefits"}]},{"type":"table","content":[{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableHeader","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Benefit"}]}]},{"type":"tableHeader","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Description"}]}]}]},{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Enhanced reasoning"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Handles multi-step reasoning, logical analysis, and complex problem solving"}]}]}]},{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Transparency"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"You see Claude's step-by-step thought process via "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"code"}],"text":"thinking"},{"type":"text","text":" blocks"}]}]}]},{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Better accuracy"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Self-reflection improves performance on math proofs, algorithm design, debugging"}]}]}]},{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Authenticity verification"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Thinking content includes digital signatures for verifying it was generated by Claude"}]}]}]}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"How It Works"}]},{"type":"orderedList","attrs":{"start":1,"type":null},"content":[{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Enable it"},{"type":"text","text":": Set "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"code"}],"text":"thinking: {type: \"enabled\", budget_tokens: N}"},{"type":"text","text":" in the API"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Token budget"},{"type":"text","text":": "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"code"}],"text":"budget_tokens"},{"type":"text","text":" determines how many tokens Claude can use for internal reasoning (e.g., 2,000 for simple problems, 10,000 for complex ones)"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Response format"},{"type":"text","text":": API returns "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"code"}],"text":"thinking"},{"type":"text","text":" blocks first, then "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"code"}],"text":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" blocks"}]}]}]},{"type":"codeBlock","attrs":{"language":"json"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"content\": [\n    {\n      \"type\": \"thinking\",\n      \"thinking\": \"Let me analyze this step by step...\",\n      \"signature\": \"WaUjzkypQ2mUEVM36...\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"type\": \"text\",\n      \"text\": \"Based on my analysis...\"\n    }\n  ]\n}"}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"When to Use It"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Use extended thinking for:"},{"type":"text","text":"\n- Mathematical proofs and logical reasoning\n- Algorithm design\n- System architecture design requiring weighing multiple options\n- Debugging complex issues with multi-level dependencies\n- Strategic planning with multi-step reasoning"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Don't use it for:"},{"type":"text","text":"\n- Simple queries\n- Creative writing"}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Trade-offs"}]},{"type":"table","content":[{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableHeader","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Trade-off"}]}]},{"type":"tableHeader","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Impact"}]}]}]},{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Cost"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Thinking tokens billed at output token price; total cost = input + thinking + output"}]}]}]},{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Latency"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Takes longer than instant responses due to deliberation"}]}]}]},{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Not always needed"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"For tasks without deep reasoning, it adds cost without benefit"}]}]}]}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Supported Models"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Extended thinking works on Claude Sonnet 4.5, Sonnet 4, Sonnet 3.7, Haiku 4.5, Opus 4.1, and Opus 4. On newer models like Claude Opus 4.6/4.7/4.8 and Claude Mythos, "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"adaptive thinking"},{"type":"text","text":" is recommended instead, where the model decides dynamically how much to think."}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Best Practices"}]},{"type":"bulletList","content":[{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Start with smaller "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"code"}],"text":"budget_tokens"},{"type":"text","text":" (e.g., 2,000) for testing"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Adjust budget based on task complexity"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Monitor actual thinking content usage"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Set "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"code"}],"text":"budget_tokens"},{"type":"text","text":" less than "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"code"}],"text":"max_tokens"}]}]}]},{"type":"paragraph"}]}}
